omberg july    pm et specialty retail company overview of saks fifth avenue inc snapshot people company overview saks fifth avenue inc owns and operates retail stores to sell mens and womens fashion products in the united states the company offers women’s apparel such as dresses tops sweaters coats jackets and vests jeans pants and shorts jumpsuits skirts suits and separates active wear sleepwear and loungewear lingerie swimwear and others men’s apparel such as active wear coats and jackets dress shirts jeans pants and shorts sport shirts suits sport coats and vests sweaters and sweatshirts swimwear tshirts and polos ties and formalwear underwear and socks and sleepwear and kids apparel it also provides shoes jewelry and accessories handbags wallets and cases b saks fifth avenue inc owns and operates retail stores to sell mens and womens fashion products in the united states the company offers women’s apparel such as dresses tops sweaters coats jackets and vests jeans pants and shorts jumpsuits skirts suits and separates active wear sleepwear and loungewear lingerie swimwear and others men’s apparel such as active wear coats and jackets dress shirts jeans pants and shorts sport shirts suits sport coats and vests sweaters and sweatshirts swimwear tshirts and polos ties and formalwear underwear and socks and sleepwear and kids apparel it also provides shoes jewelry and accessories handbags wallets and cases beauty care products sports and leisure products watches grooming and cologne products and others for men women and kids and home décor bed and bath holiday dining and entertaining gourmet food kitchen travel and technology and personalization products as well as pet accessories in addition the company offers toys and gifts and furniture for kids it also sells products through its online store in the united states and internationally the company was founded in  and is based in new york new york saks fifth avenue inc operates as a subsidiary of saks incorporated det