il synonymous with its saks fifth avenue stores the decision resulted in a july  sale of its combined  proffitts and mcraes stores to belk for approximately  million on october  that same year saks announced that it was selling the  stores within its northern department store group including carson pirie scott bergners younkers herbergers and boston store to bonton stores inc for  billion the transaction was complete as of march   on august   saks incorporated announced that it had agreed to sell its upscale  parisian stores along with two regional distribution centers and birmingham corporate headquarters to belk which rebranded them under their own name in the third quarter of  on november   saks announced the closure of the unprofitable club libby lu chain in late august  the uk tabloid daily mail reported that a private equity buyer was mulling a  billion takeover bid for saks incorporated former department store groupedit specialty department store group birmingham alabama parisian inc northern department store group milwaukee wisconsin bergners boston store carson pirie scott herbergers younkers southern department store group jackson mississippi mcraes proffitts tween chicago illinois club libby lu acquisition by hbcedit on july   torontobased hudsons bay company announced that it will buy saks incorporated for usd  billion restatementsedit in march  saks announced to restate financial results from fiscal  through the third quarter of fiscal  to correct some accounting errors related to its previously recorded operating leases see alsoedit new york city portal companies portal saks fifth avenue parisian proffitts notesedit  a b c d e f g  form k saks incorporated united states securities and exchange commission   httpwwwsaksfifthavenuecomstoresinternationaljsp    corporate addresses saks incorporated retrieved on march    a b barbaro michael  saks settles with sec on overpayments the new york times issn  retrieved    saks inc settles financial reporting and r